com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/bodyguards-forced-to-chase-minister-ben-gvir-as-he-flees-his-own-security-in-the-west-bank/0000018d-79c6-d9fb-a9fd-ffdfca510000</guid></item><item><title>由于需求低迷，以色列航空公司取消了夏季飞往​​都柏林和马拉喀什的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/el-al-cancels-summer-flights-to-dublin-and-marrakech-due-to-low-demand/0000018d-79d7-d008-a9cd-fbf75bd30000</link><description>以色列航空公司坚称取消两条线路的决定完全是基于客户的需求，而不是基于爱尔兰和摩洛哥对以色列加沙战争的政治立场</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:11:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/el-al-cancels-summer-flights-to-dublin-and-marrakech-due-to-low-demand/0000018d-79d7-d008-a9cd-fbf75bd30000</guid></item><item><title>第二家以色列银行根据美国制裁封锁西岸定居者的账户</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/second-israeli-bank-blocks-west-bank-settlers-account-in-compliance-with-u-s-sanctions/0000018d-795e-de30-a5dd-79ffa4990000</link><description>以色列政府拥有的邮政银行关闭了被列入美国制裁名单的戴维·柴·哈斯代 (David Chai Hasdai) 的账户，而一天前以色列银行也采取了类似行动；以色列央行发表声明支持雷米遵守制裁的决定</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:02:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/second-israeli-bank-blocks-west-bank-settlers-account-in-compliance-with-u-s-sanctions/0000018d-795e-de30-a5dd-79ffa4990000</guid></item><item><title>新星党大屠杀受害者家属要求以色列立法者给出答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/families-of-nova-party-massacre-victims-demand-answers-from-israeli-lawmakers/0000018d-7986-d008-a9cd-fbf7fbf50000</link><description>家人在议会听证会上表示，他们没有收到有关亲人遭遇的信息，国家也没有向他们提供支持</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 15:44:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/families-of-nova-party-massacre-victims-demand-answers-from-israeli-lawmakers/0000018d-7986-d008-a9cd-fbf7fbf50000</guid></item><item><title>14 岁巴勒斯坦少年在耶路撒冷附近企图刺伤后被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/14-year-old-palestinian-shot-and-killed-after-attempted-stabbing-near-jerusalem/0000018d-79ad-d008-a9cd-fbfd97a90000</link><description>警方称，这名名叫瓦迪·奥维萨特 (Wadee&amp;#39; Oweisat) 的青少年引起了警方的怀疑，并在警方开始搜查他后试图刺伤他们。边防警察指挥官告诉官员，“这正是我对我们战士在每场比赛中的期望”</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 15:25:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/14-year-old-palestinian-shot-and-killed-after-attempted-stabbing-near-jerusalem/0000018d-79ad-d008-a9cd-fbfd97a90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的艺术和文学也压制了加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-art-and-literature-have-repressed-gaza-too/0000018d-78c4-dd6e-a98d-fce65d040000</link><description>近几十年来，以色列社会与加沙的关系日益疏远，导致其在文化上基本上被忽视，确实涉及这一问题的作品承认，只能通过军事过滤器才能看到它</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 14:02:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-art-and-literature-have-repressed-gaza-too/0000018d-78c4-dd6e-a98d-fce65d040000</guid></item><item><title>海法市试图阻止出版一本有关以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-seeks-to-block-launch-of-a-book-on-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018d-78c8-d971-a38f-79fab7e30000</link><description>居民们对即将举行的活动表示反对，该活动计划推出该书的希伯来语译本，该书讲述了两个失去亲人的父亲（一个是以色列人，另一个是巴勒斯坦人）之间的友谊故事。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-seeks-to-block-launch-of-a-book-on-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018d-78c8-d971-a38f-79fab7e30000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔国家基金的以色列律师在人质谈判中为军队提供建议；以色列国防军：“不存在利益冲突”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lawyer-to-qatari-state-fund-advises-idf-in-hostage-negotiations/0000018d-7929-d4f1-a18d-fd7954b70000</link><description>律师约瑟夫·本克尔代表卡塔尔慈善机构，这是卡塔尔政府控制的一个基金会，曾被用来向哈马斯转移资金。战争爆发后，本克尔被征召入以色列陆军预备役，担任人质谈判顾问</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:20:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lawyer-to-qatari-state-fund-advises-idf-in-hostage-negotiations/0000018d-7929-d4f1-a18d-fd7954b70000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙，一名六岁儿童躺在坦克前的尸体中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/in-gaza-a-6-year-old-lies-before-a-tank-among-the-bodies/0000018d-78b1-d4f1-a18d-fcf145400000</link><description>Hind Hamada 这个名字对以色列人来说没有任何意义。为什么会这样呢？但她的笑脸现在可能已为每个巴勒斯坦家庭所熟悉。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/in-gaza-a-6-year-old-lies-before-a-tank-among-the-bodies/0000018d-78b1-d4f1-a18d-fcf145400000</guid></item><item><title>美国是否终于揭穿了伊朗的虚张声势，对德黑兰支持的民兵进行了打击？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/is-the-u-s-finally-calling-irans-bluff-with-strikes-on-tehran-backed-militias/0000018d-78b1-dd6e-a98d-fcb3910c0000</link><description>美国最近对叙利亚、伊拉克和也门民兵组织的袭击没有具体的战略目标，也无意实现任何超出其目标的目标，但它们仍然可以重新洗牌伊朗认为自己完全控制的地区格局</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/is-the-u-s-finally-calling-irans-bluff-with-strikes-on-tehran-backed-militias/0000018d-78b1-dd6e-a98d-fcb3910c0000</guid></item><item><title>在主要捐助者因以色列指控而暂停援助后，西班牙将向近东救济工程处额外提供 380 万美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/spain-to-give-unrwa-extra-3-8-million-after-donors-suspend-aid-amid-israeli-allegations/0000018d-794d-d008-a9cd-fbfda3ce0000</link><description>邻国葡萄牙宣布向近东救济工程处提供价值100万欧元的额外援助。其外交部长写道，“在这个困难时刻，不要背弃巴勒斯坦人民”，这一点至关重要</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:01:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/spain-to-give-unrwa-extra-3-8-million-after-donors-suspend-aid-amid-israeli-allegations/0000018d-794d-d008-a9cd-fbfda3ce0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争打造了一部混乱的混搭音乐剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/the-war-in-gaza-has-created-a-chaotic-mash-up-musical/0000018d-74b8-d4f1-a18d-f4f8d56e0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，任何人都在发行歌曲，但一位从未录制过歌曲的艺术家伊丹·阿梅迪 (Idan Amedi) 成为了新闻头条。此外，一部有关六日战争的新音乐剧登陆以色列银幕</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 10:12:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/the-war-in-gaza-has-created-a-chaotic-mash-up-musical/0000018d-74b8-d4f1-a18d-f4f8d56e0000</guid></item><item><title>警方称，以色列人在贝尔谢巴袭击平民和警察后被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-shot-dead-after-attacking-civilians-and-cops-in-beer-sheva-police-say/0000018d-788f-dd6e-a98d-fcaf727a0000</link><description>嫌疑人穆尔希德·阿卜杜勒·海伊写了一封遗书，然后离开了蒂拉的家。据警方称，他袭击了路人，高喊“真主至大”，随后警察开枪射中了他的腿部。他的兄弟否认警方的说法</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 10:03:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-shot-dead-after-attacking-civilians-and-cops-in-beer-sheva-police-say/0000018d-788f-dd6e-a98d-fcaf727a0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在加沙北部重新崛起，以展示控制权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/hamas-reemerges-in-northern-gaza-in-bid-to-demonstrate-control/0000018d-7857-d971-a38f-79f7ade40000</link><description>哈马斯正试图通过加强在北部地带和加沙城与以色列国防军的战斗以及展示对平民的控制来表明该组织仍然处于控制之中。到目前为止，大部分都是示范性的</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 09:36:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/hamas-reemerges-in-northern-gaza-in-bid-to-demonstrate-control/0000018d-7857-d971-a38f-79f7ade40000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯召见以色列大使，指责克里姆林宫与哈马斯站在一起，淡化大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/russia-to-summon-israeli-ambassador-over-unacceptable-comments/0000018d-7850-dd6e-a98d-fc720cd30000</link><description>在最近接受《生意人报》采访时，哈尔佩林严厉批评俄罗斯自10月7日袭击以来对哈马斯的立场，并指责俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫“淡化”大屠杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:13:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/russia-to-summon-israeli-ambassador-over-unacceptable-comments/0000018d-7850-dd6e-a98d-fc720cd30000</guid></item><item><title>联合国秘书长任命对以色列关于近东救济工程处工作人员参与哈马斯屠杀的指控进行审查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-live/israel-awaits-hamas-response-defense-chief-to-biden-envoy-open-to-diplomacy-with-lebanon/0000018d-775c-dd6e-a98d-f77eab370000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在党内会议上告诉利库德集团议员“我们决不能结束战争，除非我们杀死哈马斯的领导层” ■ 以色列议会拒绝反对党提交的对内塔尼亚胡总理的不信任动议 ■ 美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯抵达沙特阿拉伯，第一站自10月7日以来第五次访问该地区 ■ 俄罗斯召见以色列大使，因发表“不可接受的言论”批评俄罗斯对哈马斯的立场 ■ 火箭瞄准以色列北部和南部</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 04:32:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-live/israel-awaits-hamas-response-defense-chief-to-biden-envoy-open-to-diplomacy-with-lebanon/0000018d-775c-dd6e-a98d-f77eab370000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔对《华尔街日报》的攻击不是针对白宫，而是针对内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/netnayahu-again-lets-ben-gvir-make-a-weakling-out-of-him/0000018d-75b9-dd6e-a98d-f5bb786d0000</link><description>乔·拜登并不真正关心这位极右翼以色列部长何时希望特朗普回归，并指责他的政府更愿意支持哈马斯而不是帮助以色列。但内塔尼亚胡将不得不应对这一反弹</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 01:17:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/netnayahu-again-lets-ben-gvir-make-a-weakling-out-of-him/0000018d-75b9-dd6e-a98d-f5bb786d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国对以色列的紧急援助正处于十字路口，参众两院公布了对决措施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/house-gop-standalone-bill-on-emergency-israel-aid-faces-deep-internal-opposition/0000018d-7644-d971-a38f-77f61d060000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登表示，参议院法案“为以色列提供了他们所需要的”。如果该法案未能通过，国会面临的压力只会越来越大，要求考虑通过独立于乌克兰、台湾和边境安全措施的以色列援助</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 23:07:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/house-gop-standalone-bill-on-emergency-israel-aid-faces-deep-internal-opposition/0000018d-7644-d971-a38f-77f61d060000</guid></item></channel></rss>